(44, 10, 12, 23, 65, 25, 25, NULL, 'Animal Harmony in Scripture', 'This connection highlights the theme of harmony among animals. Both passages depict a vision of peace where different creatures coexist without harm.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
